National Bank of Abu Dhabi was asked
to provide “indicative terms” for financing Emirates Telecom
Corp.’s planned acquisition of a 46 percent stake in Mobile
Telecommunications Co., said Mark Yassin, senior general manager
of corporate & investment banking division.  To contact the reporter on this story:
